name: Feast of Cabbage and Chickpea Salad
description: Snack Feast: Double-click to set out a Feast of Cabbage and Chickpea Salad to share with anyone in the area. Feast stays active for 5 minutes.

name: Thesis on Accuracy
description: Thesis: Double-click to set out a tome to share with anyone in the area. Stays active for 5 minutes.

name: Sheet of Premium Paper
description: Crafted from wood pulp and cloth. Used to make scrolls and books.

name: Unidentified Purple Dye
description: Double-click to identify a Common, Uncommon or Rare Dye from the Purple spectrum.

name: Tray of Omnomberry Compote
description: Dessert Feast: Double-click to set out a Tray of Omnomberry Compote to share with anyone in the area. Tray stays active for 5 minutes.

name: Hard Rifle Stock
description: Used to craft Rifles and Harpoon Guns.

name: Feast of Rosemary Roasted Meat
description: Meal Feast: Double-click to set out a Feast of Rosemary Roasted Meat to share with anyone in the area. Feast stays active for 5 minutes.

name: Giver's Iron-Plated Inscription
description: Used in the crafting of weapons with +Expertise and +Vitality.

name: 12 Slot Invisible Bag
description: 12 Slots. Items in this bag will never appear in a sell-to-vendor list and will not move when inventory is sorted.

name: Strong Iron Imbued Inscription
description: Used in the crafting of weapons with +Power and +Precision.
